    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. Finished in a classic metallic silver, the exterior remains vibrant, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small door ding on the passenger side\u2014typical for a well-loved car of this age. Inside, the charcoal leather upholstery is in excellent shape with no rips or stains, and the heated seats and dual-zone climate control function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is rock solid; it has been serviced every 5,000 miles, with all fluids recently flushed and a brand-new battery installed last month. The tires have about 60% tread remaining, providing a smooth and quiet ride on the highway. It starts up immediately with no warning lights on the dash. Included are two keys, the original owner\u2019s manual, and a folder of service receipts. This is a dependable, well-maintained vehicle ready for its next owner.",
