    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has definitely been well-loved. Whether you're zipping through your daily commute or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to go. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
